00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,200
Science has a clearer story about Parker Solar Probe than social media does.

2
00:00:05,200 --> 00:00:10,400
Launched in 2018, this mission dives into the Sun's outer atmosphere, revealing mysteries.

3
00:00:10,400 --> 00:00:15,200
It’s the fastest human-made object, reaching speeds over 430,000 miles per hour!

4
00:00:15,200 --> 00:00:20,000
By flying close, it studies solar winds and their impact on Earth.

5
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:23,600
Understanding the Sun could protect our technology and lives.

